===Etymology===
From Latin '''[[digitalis]]''', from '''[[digitus]]''', ''finger'' or ''toe''

==English==
===Adjective===
'''digital''' (''no comparative or superlative forms'')

# having to do with fingers or toes
# property of dealing with [[discrete]] [[values]] rather than a continuous spectrum of values.

